# Sangsom Mini-Me Project Document

## Project Overview
**Name:** Sangsom Mini-Me  
**Genre:** Educational 3D Tamagotchi-style Care Simulation  
**Target Platform:** Unity (Multi-platform deployment)  
**Development Tools:** Unity, Cursor AI, Blender (optional for 3D modeling)  
**Universe:** Minime Universe (Expandable ecosystem of educational games)

## Core Objective
Create personalized 3D mini-avatars of students registered to the school system. Students will care for their digital mini-me by completing assigned homework, playing educational side games, and managing virtual resources (coins, gems, etc.) to purchase food, outfits, and customization items through the platform.

## Gameplay Mechanics

### Core Loop
- **Care-taking System:** 90's Tamagotchi-inspired mechanics updated with modern design
- **Homework Online Assignment:** Online capabilities enabling schools to assign homework and users to interact with models from home
- **Educational Integration:** Homework completion directly affects character well-being
- **Minime Universe Games:** Educational side games that contribute resources to main character
- **Resource Management:** Earn coins and gems through academic achievements and side games
- **Virtual Economy:** Purchase food, outfits, accessories, and room upgrades
- **Multi-Account System:** Support for multiple user profiles and characters

### Minime Universe Ecosystem
- **Educational Side Games:** Standalone games that feed resources back to main Mini-Me
- **Cross-Game Currency:** Resources earned in side games transfer to main character care
- **Expandable Content:** New educational games can be added to the universe over time
- **Integrated Progress:** Academic achievements across all games contribute to Mini-Me development

### Character Requirements

#### 3D Model Specifications
- **Art Style:** Japanese animation (anime) aesthetic
- **Input Method:** 2-3 reference images fed to AI for character generation
- **File Organization:** Photos stored in folders named after the subject/student (e.g., "Leandi")
- **Rigging Requirements:**
  - Articulated joints: Head, neck, arms, legs, hips
  - Full body movement capability
  - Facial expression support (optional enhancement)

#### Customization Features
- **Scalable Eye Sizes:** Interactive scrolling bar for eye size adjustment
- **Outfits System:** Purchasable clothing with expandable wardrobe
- **Accessories:**
  - Hats and headwear
  - Jewelry (necklaces, earrings, bracelets)
  - Additional items (expandable for future content)
- **Modular Design:** Ability to add new items and outfits post-launch

#### Pre-programmed Animations
- **Dance:** Multiple dance sequences
- **Wave:** Greeting gesture
- **Wai:** Traditional Thai greeting
- **Curtsy:** Formal bow gesture
- **Bow:** Respectful greeting

